Who am I

My name's Amr. I'm a Data Analyst focused on transforming messy transactional data into actionable business insights. I specialize in Power BI, SQL, Python and Excel — cleaning data, building star schemas and creating dashboards stakeholders can use to act quickly.

During the day I work as a Lead Data Analyst at a local agency and in the evening I work on freelance projects and utilize the time to built my own products. I spent my leisure hours writing articles and poetry. Right now I'm also trying a hand at machine learning and AI. I love to learn and explore new arenas.
